data.description: Large 3000+ square foot Colonial in the desirable Longview Estates development.  Home features 5 bedrooms, 3 1/2 baths, home office, dining room, large cathedral ceiling family room with gas fireplace, eat in kitchen with granite counters & stainless steel appliances as well as 2 finished basements adding an additional 1000+ square feet of entertainment space.  The first floor of the home features a newer addition master bedroom en suite with a beautiful tile soaker tub and shower as well as 2 walk in closets and its own private finished basement.  Exterior features include a farmers porch just added this year, 2 car garage, large multi tier deck with outdoor television and pool, patio area with fire pit and a fenced in yard.  This home is a perfect solution for a large family, anyone needing a possible in-law setup or a family requiring large accommodations with a first floor bedroom suite.
